  "title": "Admin Executive (Clinic)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Respond to phone calls promptly while managing the front desk;</li>\n  <li>Serve as the first point of contact and deliver quality service to walk-in visitors;</li>\n  <li>Support doctors and nurses by preparing patients for their consultations;</li>\n  <li>Assist with ordering and tracking diagnostic tests to ensure a smooth patient experience;</li>\n  <li>Ensure documents are updated accurately and promptly in the clinic system and properly handled at the front desk;</li>\n  <li>Help process billing correctly and efficiently;</li>\n  <li>Follow through on each patient’s full visit, including scheduling their next appointment when required;</li>\n  <li>Prepare for the clinic’s operations for the following day.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Business Administration or any related field.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1 year working experience in healthcare industry</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly email an updated copy of your resume to: <strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com;</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p>\n<p>Registration No.: R23117856 CHOE KIN MUN</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
